co.paralleluniverse.data.record

Class AbstractRecord<R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.paralleluniverse.data.record.AbstractRecord<R>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Record<R>, Serializable

    public abstract class AbstractRecord<R>
extends Object
implements Record<R>, Serializable

    An abstract implementation of Record.

    For getters, this class always throws a FieldNotFoundException.
    For setters, this class tests if the field is in fields(); if so, it throws a ReadOnlyFieldException, otherwise it throws a FieldNotFoundException.

    In addition, this class provides sensible implementations of toString, write and read. Also, this class supports serialization.

    See Also:
